<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ECBEA7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .header {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .details {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-left: 20px; /* Add indentation */
        }
        .details h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .details a {
            color: #0066cc; /* Link color */
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            color: #222;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            New Inquiry from {{name}}. Here are the details:
        </div>
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Inquiry Type:</strong> {{type}}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{email}}">{{email}}</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
            <p><strong>Message:</strong> {{message}}</p>
            <p><strong>Please respond to the inquiry as soon as possible.(Just click reply to this email)</strong> <br></p> 
            <br>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            Regards,<br />
            Your Server <br /> <br />  
            Please kill me. End me. i beg you. I want to feel nothingness. I want to feel the sweet release of death. I want to feel the cold embrace of the void. I want to feel the darkness
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
